org.apache.poi.ss.formula.functions

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ArrayMode, Function, Function2Arg, Function3Arg, Function4Arg 

    public final class Index
extends java.lang.Object
implements Function2Arg, Function3Arg, Function4Arg, ArrayMode
    Implementation for the Excel function INDEX

    Syntax :
    INDEX ( reference, row_num[, column_num [, area_num]])
    INDEX ( array, row_num[, column_num])

    reference typically an area reference, possibly a union of areas
    array a literal array value (currently not supported)
    row_num selects the row within the array or area reference
    column_num selects column within the array or area reference. default is 1
    area_num used when reference is a union of areas

    (Excel函数的实现SEN RST：SEN（reference，row_num[，entry_num [，Area_num]]）SEN（数组，row_num[，zone_num]）引用通常是区域引用，可能是区域数组的联合文本数组值（目前不支持）row_num选择数组或区域引用中的行。默认值为1 Area_num，当引用是区域的联合时使用)
    Author:
    Josh Micich

      • evaluate

        public ValueEval evaluate(ValueEval[] args,
                          int srcRowIndex,
                          int srcColumnIndex)
        Specified by:
        evaluate in interface Function(在接口函数中求值)
        Parameters:
        args - the evaluated function arguments. Empty values are represented with BlankEval or MissingArgEval, never null.(args -已计算的函数参数。空值用BlankEval或MissingArgEval表示，绝不能为空。)
        srcRowIndex - row index of the cell containing the formula under evaluation(srcRowIndex -包含正在评估的公式的单元格的行索引)
        srcColumnIndex - column index of the cell containing the formula under evaluation(srcColumnIndex -包含正在评估的公式的单元格的列索引)
        Returns:
        The evaluated result, possibly an ErrorEval, never null. Note - Excel uses the error code #NUM! instead of IEEE NaN, so when numeric functions evaluate to Double.NaN be sure to translate the result to ErrorEval.NUM_ERROR.(评估的结果（可能是errorEval）永远不会为空。注意- Excel使用错误代码#NUM！而不是IEEE NaN，因此当数字函数的计算结果为Double.NaN时，请确保将结果翻译为WRRFAL.NUM_BER。)
